channel.title: People cant connect to IP? (Please Help!)
channel.description:
I just port forwarded on my computer and also went through the NO-Ip process. Now, whenever I run my server, it is able to be connected to but I think as soon as people connect to it, it kicks them. I think this because when I got to my Run.bat it shows this:
Connection from *Their IP appears here* Null has logged out.
But it never said anyone has logged in. I think my computer is rejecting their connections but IDK how to fix it! please help!
